summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 3782, entitled "An Ordinance to regulate the business of plumbing, steam fitting, and gas fitting in the City of Seattle and providing a penalty for the violation of the provisions thereof, repealing Ordinance No. 1604 entitled "An Ordinance to regulate the business of plumbing, steam fitting, and gas fitting in the City of Seattle," approved 24th day of January, 1891," approved April 17, 1895.
